SupplementalInformationDetail.ExplanationTxt: MICHIGAN GARDEN CLUBS (THE CLUB) PROVIDES LEADERSHIP AND EDUCATION, RESOURCES, AND NETWORKING OPPORTUNITIES FOR ITS MEMBERS TO PROMOTE THE LOVE OF GARDENING, FLORAL AND LANDSCAPE DESIGN, AND ENVIRONMENTAL RESPONSIBILITY.
EACH MEMBER HAS A REPRESENTATIVE THAT VOTES AT THE ANNUAL MEETING.
THE MEMBERS VOTE AND ELECT THE OFFICERS AND BOARD MEMBERS.
THE EXECUTIVE COMMITTEE REVIEWS THE FORM 990 PRIOR TO SUBMISSION TO THE IRS. THE FORM 990 IS AVAILABLE FOR ALL THE BOARD OF DIRECTORS ON THE BOARD SIDE OF OUR WEBSITE.
DOCUMENTS ARE MADE PUBLIC TO ANYONE UPON WRITTEN REQUEST.
